data.description: Discover the pleasure of living in 2001 Bluebird Way, a well-maintained four-bedroom, two-bath ranch home on a spacious corner lot. You will be welcome with a roomy and bright floor plan, a  wood-burning fireplace, a sizeable living room, and a separate dining room. The new living room sliding glass door opens to a large backyard, offering a blank canvas for your vision. The home also offers original hardwood floors throughout, new Samsung smart appliances, lots of storage, plenty of parking, and closet space with cedar-lined flooring. It is a great opportunity and an excellent fit for first-time homebuyers or investors.
